  "stem": "<p>What is the equation of the line that passes through the point (0, 9) and is parallel to the graph of <i>y</i> = 4<i>x</i> &minus; 2 in the <i>xy</i>-plane?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><i>y</i> = 9<i>x</i> + 4</p>"
