  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Parallel lines share a slope, so the slope is 4. The line passes through (0, 9), so the <i>y</i>-intercept is 9. Thus <i>y</i> = 4<i>x</i> + 9.</p><p>Choices A and B use 9 as the slope. Choice D omits the <i>y</i>-intercept.</p>",
